{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/uk-space-agency/about","content_id":"5f5a2119-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"The UK Space Agency sets the national direction on space.","details":{"attachments":[{"accessible":false,"alternative_format_contact_email":"correspondence@dsit.gov.uk","assets":[{"asset_manager_id":"5a7f6c30ed915d74e33f6554","filename":"UK-Space-Agency-logos.zip"}],"attachment_type":"file","content_type":"application/zip","file_size":3232145,"filename":"UK-Space-Agency-logos.zip","id":"9219612","title":"UK Space Agency logo","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a7f6c30ed915d74e33f6554/UK-Space-Agency-logos.zip"},{"accessible":false,"alternative_format_contact_email":"correspondence@dsit.gov.uk","assets":[{"asset_manager_id":"5a74b81ced915d4d83b5e651","filename":"UK_Space_Agency_-_Branding_Guidelines.pdf"}],"attachment_type":"file","content_type":"application/pdf","file_size":4238623,"filename":"UK_Space_Agency_-_Branding_Guidelines.pdf","id":"9219613","number_of_pages":32,"title":"Branding Guidelines ","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a74b81ced915d4d83b5e651/UK_Space_Agency_-_Branding_Guidelines.pdf"}],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The UK Space Agency coheres policy, strategy and delivery across the whole of government, driving innovation and delivering world-class space science programmes in partnership with the UK space sector and international partners. </p>\n\n<p>The UK space sector generates an annual income of £18.6 billion and employs 55,000 people across the country.  More generally, space and satellite services are estimated to support wider industrial activities worth £454 billion to the economy, or 18% of GDP. </p>\n\n<p>The UK Space Agency is part of the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology. We work closely with other departments and research organisations which have equities in space.</p>\n\n<div class=\"call-to-action\">\n  <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/uk-space-agency-annual-report-and-accounts-2024-2025\">Read our latest Annual Report</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"Updated with information now the UK Space Agency has merged into DSIT.","public_timestamp":"2026-04-01T11:28:17Z"},{"note":"Updated to reflect new organisational information.","public_timestamp":"2025-11-14T15:13:20Z"},{"note":"Updated with latest figures.","public_timestamp":"2025-08-18T09:48:37Z"},{"note":"Updated industry statistics","public_timestamp":"2024-07-29T10:31:08Z"},{"note":"Updated with new wording on UK Space Agency role and purpose.","public_timestamp":"2024-02-02T14:20:32Z"},{"note":"Updated income and employment figures.","public_timestamp":"2023-03-30T11:19:09Z"},{"note":"Added Respectful Behaviour Policy link.","public_timestamp":"2022-09-28T14:33:02Z"},{"note":"Updated with information on Corporate Plan and Priorities.","public_timestamp":"2022-08-05T14:08:46Z"},{"note":"Updated page to include new links to programme page, a summary (to appear on UKSA homepage) and general rewrite. ","public_timestamp":"2022-04-01T16:12:06Z"},{"note":"Updated with 2021 mission statement.","public_timestamp":"2021-04-19T14:03:03Z"},{"note":"Updated corporate plan","public_timestamp":"2021-03-29T10:39:44Z"},{"note":"Committees removed and added to Our Governance.","public_timestamp":"2018-11-22T15:14:35Z"},{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2014-05-12T09:39:58Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[{"contents":["f69bf4eb-8d2d-4d87-b0f8-ab0ca2cea9fd"],"name":"Access our information"},{"contents":["5f56454c-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef"],"name":"Jobs and contracts"}],"organisation":"1a22a221-513b-4a8d-ae97-e3668b6d5568","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2014-05-12T11:39:58+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/uk-space-agency/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/orga